{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01K3BwDBXXg1hHyopzaHRMMb","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! I have all the information you need. Let me create a comprehensive summary:\n\n## Summary of CoinflipRoundPage Component and Route Registration\n\n### 1. **CoinflipRoundPage Component** (Full Content)\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/pages/CoinflipRoundPage.tsx` (160 lines)\n\n**Key Features**:\n- Displays fairness proof for a Coinflip round after settlement\n- Fetches round data from `VITE_FAIRNESS_BACKEND_URL/fairness/rounds/by-id/{matchId}`\n- Shows commit-reveal cryptographic verification information\n- Renders different content based on phase (pending vs. settled)\n- Includes a reusable `Row` helper component for displaying key-value pairs with copy-to-clipboard functionality\n\n**Main States**:\n- Loading, error, and round data states\n- Displays round info, commitment, and (when settled) secret, entropy, result hash, winner, payout, and settlement transaction\n\n---\n\n### 2. **Route Registration in App.tsx**\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/App.tsx`\n\n**Route Definition** (line 382):\n```typescript\n<Route path=\"/coinflip/:matchId/proof\" element={<CoinflipRoundPage />} />\n```\n\n**Related Routes**:\n- `<Route path=\"/coinflip\" element={<CoinflipPage />} />` (line 371)\n- `<Route path=\"/coinflip/:matchId\" element={<CoinflipPage />} />` (line 372) — passes matchId to CoinflipPage\n- `<Route path=\"/lord-of-rngs/:matchId/proof\" element={<LordRoundPage />} />` (line 383) — similar pattern for Lord of RNGs\n\n**Import** (line 17):\n```typescript\nimport { CoinflipRoundPage } from \"./pages/CoinflipRoundPage\";\n```\n\n---\n\n### 3. **RoundData Interface (Types)**\n\n**CoinflipRoundPage RoundData** (lines 9-28):\n```typescript\ninterface RoundData {\n  pda: string;\n  game: string;\n  phase: string;                    // \"settled\" or other phases\n  creator: string;\n  commitment: string;\n  amountLamports: number;\n  matchId: string;\n  createdAt: string;\n  updatedAt: string;\n  side?: number;                    // 0 = Heads, 1 = Tails\n  secret?: string;\n  resultHash?: string | null;\n  resultSide?: number | null;\n  winner?: string | null;\n  settleTx?: string | null;\n  entropy?: string | null;\n  payoutAmount?: number | null;\n  feeAmount?: number | null;\n}\n```\n\n**LordRoundPage RoundData** (lines 9-30 in LordRoundPage.tsx) — extends above with:\n- `winningOffset?: string | null;`\n- `winningEntryIndex?: number | null;`\n- `rentRefund?: number | null;`\n- `totalAmountLamports?: number | null;`\n\n---\n\n### 4. **API Calls**\n\n**Backend URL Configuration**:\n```typescript\nconst FAIRNESS_BACKEND_URL = (\n  (import.meta as unknown as { env: Record<string, string | undefined> }).env\n    .VITE_FAIRNESS_BACKEND_URL ?? \"http://127.0.0.1:3100\"\n).replace(/\\/$/, \"\");\n```\n\n**Fetch Endpoint**:\n```typescript\nfetch(`${FAIRNESS_BACKEND_URL}/fairness/rounds/by-id/${matchId}`)\n```\n\n---\n\n### 5. **Related Components and Context**\n\n- **CoinflipPage**: Main game interface that references round history and likely links to fairness proof\n- **LordRoundPage**: Parallel component for Lord of RNGs using the same fairness backend pattern\n- **FairnessPage**: Hub for fairness verification tools (line 381: `/fairness`)\n- **CoinflipContext**: Manages game state for Coinflip matches\n\n---\n\n### 6. **Key Implementation Details**\n\n- **No URL generation in component**: The component uses `useParams` to extract `matchId` from URL\n- **Controlled error states**: Shows specific messages for 404 vs. other errors\n- **Conditional rendering**: Different UI for pending (commitment locked) vs. settled (full reveal) phases\n- **Hardcoded conversion**: `LAMPORTS_PER_SOL = 1_000_000_000` for amount formatting\n- **External links**: Settlement transaction links to Solana Explorer with `?cluster=devnet`\n- **Copy-to-clipboard**: Addresses and hashes can be copied via click\n\nAll file paths are absolute paths relative to the repository root."},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: a282942ef941841c1 (for resuming to continue this agent's work if needed)\n<usage>total_tokens: 54507\ntool_uses: 8\nduration_ms: 46449</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"89d4f6ce-bf36-4167-ba30-a196c35784b5","uuid":"c72d3d8c-a908-4f01-bb76-3291884dcc35","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Find and read the CoinflipRoundPage component and its route registration. I need:\n1. The full content of the CoinflipRoundPage component file\n2. The route definition in App.tsx for `/coinflip/:matchId`\n3. Any related types or API calls used\n\nLook in `sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/` for these files. Be thorough - read the full file contents.\n","agentId":"a282942ef941841c1","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! I have all the information you need. Let me create a comprehensive summary:\n\n## Summary of CoinflipRoundPage Component and Route Registration\n\n### 1. **CoinflipRoundPage Component** (Full Content)\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/pages/CoinflipRoundPage.tsx` (160 lines)\n\n**Key Features**:\n- Displays fairness proof for a Coinflip round after settlement\n- Fetches round data from `VITE_FAIRNESS_BACKEND_URL/fairness/rounds/by-id/{matchId}`\n- Shows commit-reveal cryptographic verification information\n- Renders different content based on phase (pending vs. settled)\n- Includes a reusable `Row` helper component for displaying key-value pairs with copy-to-clipboard functionality\n\n**Main States**:\n- Loading, error, and round data states\n- Displays round info, commitment, and (when settled) secret, entropy, result hash, winner, payout, and settlement transaction\n\n---\n\n### 2. **Route Registration in App.tsx**\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/App.tsx`\n\n**R