{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_016iMb2MXhB6BZWgzawVCtjg","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Excellent! I have all the information needed. Let me provide a comprehensive summary of the findings.\n\n## Summary\n\nI've found and read the LordOfRngs deep-link pages for the Lord of RNGs game (Jackpot). Here are the key files:\n\n### Route Definitions (App.tsx)\n- **`/lord-of-rngs`** → `<LordOfRngsPage />` - Main game page\n- **`/lord-of-rngs/:matchId`** → `<LordOfRngsPage />` - Deep-link to load a specific round by matchId\n- **`/lord-of-rngs/:matchId/proof`** → `<LordRoundPage />` - Fairness proof page for a specific round\n\n### LordOfRngsPage.tsx\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/pages/LordOfRngsPage.tsx` (552 lines)\n\nThis is the main game page with three content views:\n1. **TierLobby** - Shows open rounds available to join\n2. **TierRoundView** - Shows a selected round with join controls\n3. **ActiveRoundView** - Shows the active round the user is playing in\n\nKey features:\n- Wager input for entry amounts\n- Round selection and joining\n- Active round status tracking (waiting, countdown, spinning, revealing, complete)\n- \"Buy Entry\" button to add more entries to active rounds\n- Sidebar with round stats (players, entries, pool, odds)\n- Fairness proof links per round (see below)\n- History modal showing past rounds with results\n- Victory detection and payout display\n\n### LordRoundPage.tsx\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/pages/LordRoundPage.tsx` (171 lines)\n\nThis is the **fairness proof/verification page** for a completed round. Accessible via deep-links like:\n- `/lord-of-rngs/:matchId/proof`\n\nFeatures:\n- Fetches round data from `GET /fairness/rounds/by-id/:matchId`\n- Displays commit-reveal proof details:\n  - **Before settlement**: Shows commitment hash (locked)\n  - **After settlement**: Shows all verification data:\n    - Secret (server seed)\n    - Entropy (from SlotHashes sysvar)\n    - Result hash\n    - Winning offset\n    - Winning entry index\n    - Winner address\n    - Payout amount & fees\n    - Settlement transaction hash (links to Solana devnet explorer)\n- Includes verification instructions showing how to manually verify:\n  - `SHA-256(secret) = commitment`\n  - `Result = SHA-256(secret || entropy || pda || algorithm_version)`\n  - Winning offset calculation: `result_hash[0..8] as u64 mod total_pool`\n  - Entry selection: \"Entries are walked in order until cumulative amount exceeds offset\"\n- Clickable fields for copying hash values\n\n### Key Integration Points\n- Round data interface includes: pda, game, phase, creator, commitment, amountLamports, matchId, createdAt, updatedAt, secret, resultHash, winner, settleTx, entropy, winningOffset, winningEntryIndex, payoutAmount, feeAmount, rentRefund, totalAmountLamports\n- Links from `LordOfRngsPage` → `LordRoundPage` via \"Verify fairness\" links on every round\n- Main fairness backend endpoint: `/fairness/rounds/by-id/:matchId` (configurable via `VITE_FAIRNESS_BACKEND_URL`)\n\nAll files are located in `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/`."},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: ad0d7718cce6d0095 (for resuming to continue this agent's work if needed)\n<usage>total_tokens: 56701\ntool_uses: 8\nduration_ms: 43977</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"89d4f6ce-bf36-4167-ba30-a196c35784b5","uuid":"cd3a2b73-616b-46d1-8c5c-1792cbf14617","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Find and read the LordOfRngsRoundPage or similar deep-link page for lord-of-rngs. Look in `sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/lord-of-rngs/` and check for a `pages/` directory or round page component. Read the full content. Also check `sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/App.tsx` for the route definitions for lord-of-rngs.\n","agentId":"ad0d7718cce6d0095","content":[{"type":"text","text":"