 address\n    - Payout amount & fees\n    - Settlement transaction hash (links to Solana devnet explorer)\n- Includes verification instructions showing how to manually verify:\n  - `SHA-256(secret) = commitment`\n  - `Result = SHA-256(secret || entropy || pda || algorithm_version)`\n  - Winning offset calculation: `result_hash[0..8] as u64 mod total_pool`\n  - Entry selection: \"Entries are walked in order until cumulative amount exceeds offset\"\n- Clickable fields for copying hash values\n\n### Key Integration Points\n- Round data interface includes: pda, game, phase, creator, commitment, amountLamports, matchId, createdAt, updatedAt, secret, resultHash, winner, settleTx, entropy, winningOffset, winningEntryIndex, payoutAmount, feeAmount, rentRefund, totalAmountLamports\n- Links from `LordOfRngsPage` → `LordRoundPage` via \"Verify fairness\" links on every round\n- Main fairness backend endpoint: `/fairness/rounds/by-id/:matchId` (configurable via `VITE_FAIRNESS_BACKEND_URL`)\n\nAll files are located in `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/`."}],"totalDurationMs":43977,"totalTokens":56701,"totalToolUseCount":8,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":328,"cache_read_input_tokens":55456,"output_tokens":915,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":328},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
