{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01WS32LLD5VBtgSSoY61FRSo","type":"tool_result","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! I have all the information I need. Let me now provide a comprehensive summary.\n\n## Summary: Close Call Feature Files Analysis\n\n### 1. Directory Structure\n\n```\n/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/close-call/\n├── components/\n│   ├── ActiveBetView.tsx\n│   ├── BetAmountInput.tsx\n│   ├── CandlestickChart.tsx\n│   ├── PoolDistribution.tsx\n│   ├── RoundResultOverlay.tsx\n│   ├── SideSelector.tsx\n│   └── index.ts\n├── context/\n│   └── CloseCallContext.tsx\n├── hooks/\n│   └── index.ts\n├── utils/\n│   └── payout-calculator.ts\n├── data/\n│   └── btc-candles.json\n├── types.ts\n└── index.ts\n\n/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/pages/\n├── CloseCallPage.tsx  (MAIN GAME PAGE - already exists)\n└── (No CloseCallRoundPage yet - needs to be created)\n```\n\n### 2. Types.ts (Current Version)\n\n**File**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/close-call/types.ts`\n\nKey types:\n- `BetSide`: \"green\" | \"red\"\n- `RoundPhase`: \"open\" | \"settled\" | \"refunded\"\n- `CandleOutcome`: \"green\" | \"red\" | \"refund\"\n- `Candle`: OHLC data with timestamps\n- `PlayerBet`: Individual bet (address, side, amount, timestamp)\n- `PoolState`: Tracking of both pools and player bets\n- `Round`: Complete round data (id, phase, pool, timing, result, oracle prices, settlement)\n- `UserRoundHistory`: User's history entry with round, bet, payout, and won status\n- `CloseCallContextValue`: Full context API\n\nConstants defined:\n- `DEFAULT_BET_AMOUNT = 0.5 SOL`\n- `MIN_BET_AMOUNT = 0.001 SOL`\n- `MAX_BET_AMOUNT = 100 SOL`\n- `PLATFORM_FEE_BPS = 300` (3%)\n- `CANDLE_DURATION_MS = 60000`\n- `BETTING_WINDOW_MS = 30000`\n- `SIDE_COLORS`: green \"#45b058\", red \"#dc3545\", refund \"#f0b820\"\n\n### 3. Existing Round History Component & Modal\n\n**Location**: `/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/pages/CloseCallPage.tsx`\n\nThe CloseCallPage already has:\n- `selectedHistory` state for modal management (line 39)\n- `historyEntries` array converted from `userHistory` (lines 49-72)\n- History modal showing detailed round info (lines 250-358)\n- Modal displays:\n  - Round stats (your side, stake, outcome, result, payout)\n  - Candle data (open, close, change)\n  - Oracle verification section with round ID, oracle name, settlement tx\n  - Link to fairness page: `/fairness`\n\n**Key History Modal Features**:\n- Result formatting with styled colors\n- Candle outcome colors\n- Win/loss status with green/red colors\n- Payout amount formatting\n- Settlement transaction link with explorer\n\n### 4. CloseCallPage.tsx Structure\n\nThe main game page:\n- Uses `GameLayout` component with sidebar + history panel\n- Converts `UserRoundHistory[]` to `HistoryEntry[]` format for the UI\n- Each history entry has:\n  - `roundId`: Last 8 chars of full round ID\n  - `result`: Styled JSX with side color and WIN/LOST text\n  - `payout`: Won amount or negative loss amount\n  - `timestamp`: Resolution time\n  - `verified`: true\n  - `won`: boolean flag\n  - `onClick`: Opens the history modal\n\n**History Entry Styling**:\n```jsx\nresult: (\n  <span className=\"close-call-history-result\">\n    <span style={{ color: sideColor, textShadow: `0 0 4px ${sideColor}` }}>\n      {entry.userBet.side.toUpperCase()}\n    </span>\n    <span className=\"close-call-history-result__separator\">|</span>\n    <span style={{ color: outcomeColor, textShadow: `0 0 4px ${outcomeColor}` }}>\n      {entry.won ? \"WON\" : \"LOST\"}\n    </span>\n  </span>\n)\n```\n\n### 5. Pages Directory Status\n\n**Existing Pages**:\n- `/pages/CloseCallPage.tsx` - Main game page (no deep-link support yet)\n- `/pages/CoinflipPage.tsx`\n- `/pages/CoinflipRoundPage.tsx` - Proof/fairness page (example)\n- `/pages/LordOfRngsPage.tsx`\n- `/pages/LordRoundPage.tsx` - Proof/fairness page (example)\n- `/pages/CryptoCrashPage.tsx`\n- `/pages/GameOfTradesPage.tsx`\n- `/pages/FairnessPage.tsx`\n- `/pages/QuestsPage.tsx`\n- `/pages/LootPage.tsx`\n\n**No pages directory exists inside close-call feature** - pages are at the app level.\n\n### 6. Routing Pattern (from App.tsx)\n\nCurrent routes:\n```tsx\n<Route path=\"/close-call\" element={<CloseCallPage />} />\n```\n\nPattern from other games (coinflip/lord-of-rngs):\n```tsx\n<Route path=\"/coinflip/:matchId\" element={<CoinflipPage />} />\n<Route path=\"/coinflip/:matchId/proof\" element={<CoinflipRoundPage />} />\n<Route path=\"/lord-of-rngs/:matchId\" element={<LordOfRngsPage />} />\n<Route path=\"/lord-of-rngs/:matchId/proof\" element={<LordRoundPage />} />\n```\n\n### 7. History Entry Format (from @rng-utopia/ui)\n\n**Type**: `HistoryEntry` from `/packages/ui/src/layouts/HistoryPanel.tsx`\n\n```typescript\ninterface HistoryEntry {\n  roundId: string;           // Displayed as #roundId\n  result: ReactNode;         // Custom JSX/text\n  payout?: number;           // Formatted as $X.XXXX\n  timestamp: Date;           // Shown as \"Xm ago\", \"Xh ago\", etc.\n  verified?: boolean;        // Shows ✓ checkmark\n  won?: boolean;             // Applies \"rng-history-item--won\" CSS class\n  onClick?: () => void;      // Makes item clickable\n}\n```\n\n### 8. Backend API Integration (from CloseCallContext)\n\n- **Current round**: `GET /closecall/current-round`\n- **History**: `GET /closecall/history?limit=20`\n- **Response format**: `BackendRoundResponse` with entries arrays, phase, outcome, prices\n- **Polling**: Every 2 seconds for round state\n- **History polling**: Loads on address change and phase transitions\n\n### 9. Key Observations for Deep-Link Implementation\n\n1. **No existing deep-link page for Close Call** - CoinflipRoundPage and LordRoundPage serve as templates\n2. **Round ID format**: 16-char hex string (8 bytes), stored in backend as `roundId`\n3. **API endpoint available**: `GET /fairness/rounds/by-id/{roundId}` (used by LordRoundPage)\n4. **History modal already exists** but needs to link to a dedicated proof page\n5. **Modal layout shows all fairness data needed** - Oracle prices, settlement tx, round ID\n6. **Similar oracle-based game** - CloseCall uses Pyth (vs commit-reveal for Coinflip/Lord)\n\n### 10. Components Not Yet Exported\n\nThe `ActiveBetView.tsx` and `RoundResultOverlay.tsx` are in components but used inline - not exported in index.ts\n\n---\n\n**Files to Create for Deep-Link Support**:\n1. `CloseCallRoundPage.tsx` in `/pages/` (proof/fairness page)\n2. Update routing in `App.tsx` to add `/close-call/:roundId` route\n3. Update CloseCallPage history modal to link to the new page"},{"type":"text","text":"agentId: a64d4afb53d564882 (for resuming to continue this agent's work if needed)\n<usage>total_tokens: 78035\ntool_uses: 24\nduration_ms: 57708</usage>"}]}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"89d4f6ce-bf36-4167-ba30-a196c35784b5","uuid":"730cc482-c39b-47da-99cf-22d399357249","tool_use_result":{"status":"completed","prompt":"Find and read the close-call feature files in `sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/close-call/`. I need:\n1. The directory structure (all files)\n2. The content of `types.ts` (current version)\n3. Any existing round history component that would need to link to the deep-link page\n4. The CloseCallPage.tsx to see how history is shown\n5. Check if there's a `pages/` directory already\n\nBe thorough - read file contents, not just list files.\n","agentId":"a64d4afb53d564882","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Perfect! I have all the information I need. Let me now provide a comprehensive summary.\n\n## Summary: Close Call Feature Files Analysis\n\n### 1. Directory Structure\n\n```\n/workspaces/rng-utopia/sources/rng-utopia/apps/platform/src/features/close-call/\n├── components/\n│   ├── ActiveBetView.tsx\n│   ├── BetAmountInput.tsx\n│   ├── CandlestickChart.tsx\n│   ├── P